episodes.name: What Is Love?
episodes.overview: The men are all smiles when the women finally make an appearance. Professional fighter Taiju doesn't waste any time showing his feelings.

episodes.name: Another Wolf
episodes.overview: The first Sun LINE leads to a complicated double date. Meanwhile, Masaki and Honoka go and visit Taiju, who is practicing for an upcoming match.

episodes.name: A Love That Can't Last
episodes.overview: Who-ya takes his date out for a casual day of shopping, but a surprise visitor makes an appearance. It's the day of Tajiu’s RISE match, and all members tune in.

episodes.name: A Love Running Out of Time
episodes.overview: The men find out that they'll have to vote on who they think the wolf might be, and the woman who receives the most votes will have to go home.

episodes.name: Can You Lie to the One You Love?
episodes.overview: Now halfway through their "Wolf" journey, the women must confess their feelings. Meanwhile, the men bear the heavy burden of casting their votes.

episodes.name: A Wish Upon the Falling Cherry Blossoms
episodes.overview: Sakurako, Tomoki and Robin head to cherry-blossom-filled Aomori to take a photo. Later, someone uses the more secretive Moon LINE for the first time.

episodes.name: A Wish Made with Hands Intertwined
episodes.overview: Gabby plans a date by the sea. For her photoshoot, Julie takes an overnight trip to a breathtaking island, and she asks one person to accompany her.

episodes.name: If I Can't See You Again
episodes.overview: While gathered together for a barbecue, the group learns that the voting results will finally be announced after the sun sets that night.

episodes.name: Can't Get Back That Smile
episodes.overview: Gabby leaves for her sunrise photoshoot in Hokkaido. Julie receives an emotional gift. Honoka confides in a few women members for advice.

episodes.name: Tell Me Your Lies
episodes.overview: To help clear the air, Tomoki comes up with an ingenious plan. For her photoshoot, Mikako suggests a double date. Who-ya invites everyone to his concert.

episodes.name: One Last Time, One Last Lie
episodes.overview: The members go to Niigata for their last photoshoot. With time running out, everyone makes their final moves before the wolf — or wolves — are revealed.

episodes.name: Don't Run Out of Love
episodes.overview: With a red balloon in hand, each woman awaits the final confessions of love. If she’s a wolf, she must release her balloon into the sky.
